opam-version: "2.0"
synopsis: "Anthropic Messages API client"
description:
  "Anthropic Messages API client over llm-core. Tool use (JSON Schema), prompt caching, system prompts, and refusal handling. HTTP-client- and runtime-agnostic via the llm-core CPS interface."
maintainer: ["sabine@makerprism.com"]
authors: ["Sabine Schmaltz"]
license: "MIT"
homepage: "https://github.com/makerprism/ocaml-llm-sdk"
